&ldquo;Don&rsquo;t be so loud, someone will hear us.&rdquo;
&ldquo;YOU DON’T KNOW THAT ANYMORE! Other planets don’t sneak onto other planets anymore now tha-&rdquo; When she heard no answer, she pivoted toward where Sproon used to be.
